text: "Atingkok" () (literally, "father void") is the Supreme Creator God of the universe in Meitei mythology and religion. He is regarded as the legendary male ancestor of the living beings on the earth. ==Related pages== * List of figures in Meitei mythology ==Further reading== * * == References == == Other websites == Category:Kings in Meitei mythology Category:Meitei gods and goddesses Category:Gods and goddesses of the sky
title: Atingkok
